{"tid":2235203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"23年來最高官階 朝駐意代辦投韓","createTime":"2020-10-08T13:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T14:18:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4d670e8849e0467c04af5241b45337cc0d922e65","tid":2235203,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201008/VPG4SG3MFJG4DCHFRZQXBEWTEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201008%2FVPG4SG3MFJG4DCHFRZQXBEWTEA%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=43e18036\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201008%2FVPG4SG3MFJG4DCHFRZQXBEWTEA%2F&h=59be9a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201008/VPG4SG3MFJG4DCHFRZQXBEWTEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n23年來最高官階 朝駐意代辦投韓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UZhUxm0NBDxfpuE7ExHl_uYO7Nk=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NZWKVTGHENBA5GQAKHPW6QW6KY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUZhUxm0NBDxfpuE7ExHl_uYO7Nk%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNZWKVTGHENBA5GQAKHPW6QW6KY.jpg&h=2a5ee9b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曹成吉（右二）已投奔南韓。<br />\n<br />\n北韓前駐意大利臨時代辦曹成吉（Jo Song Gil，音譯）前年11月離開當地大使館後失蹤。南韓國會情報委員會昨日證實，他去年7月投奔南韓，是23年來投奔南韓的最高級北韓官員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7月攜妻抵埗 女兒仍在朝<br />\n<br />\n南韓國會情報委員會委員長全海澈證實，曹成吉屢次表明希望投奔南韓，並於去年7月帶同妻子抵埗，但因為擔心留在北韓家人的安全，故不願向外公佈投奔南韓。全海澈又指，在傳媒前一日報道曹成吉入境南韓的消息前，國家情報院已向國會情報委員會滙報，但以保護人身安全為由，未有交代曹成吉流亡動機和途徑，以及現時住所等。<br />\n<br />\n意大利政府2017年9月以北韓進行第六次核試為由，驅逐時任北韓駐意大利大使文正南出境，曹成吉其後成為臨時代辦，惟上任不足一個月離開大使館後失蹤，當時分析相信他可能在意大利等外國政府庇護下準備流亡第三國。意大利外交部去年2月證實，曹成吉的未成年女兒從意大利返回平壤。<br />\n<br />\n反對派議員趙太庸批評，若非政府和情報部門協助，根本無可能證實曹成吉流亡的消息，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n曹成吉是前北韓勞動黨書記黃長燁1997年變節後投奔南韓後的最高級北韓官員，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"54cc11e554b068d48f74e6fc54858ae847fc7081","tid":2235203,"uid":370061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"唔洗食草lu~"},{"pid":"b2496116d769991fd0549c1f7d07bc368b8ad0b2","tid":2235203,"uid":72173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"脫北原因: 可以換過個整容南韓老婆了"},{"pid":"6ac8f39d4392ade49ca6bd631518fd8263a3ef04","tid":2235203,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:32:55.000Z","msg":"金仔又嬲嬲豬要射野"},{"pid":"febb8816a794827711941fe078c340f63291e09b","tid":2235203,"uid":90499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"留低個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dba3519b7fe1077d948a92fd55a694bd4b6f90","tid":2235203,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"女兒仍在朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8890a9c6b5081404e0bb7075835475fa5d490c3c","tid":2235203,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>意大利外交部去年2月證實，曹成吉的未成年女兒從意大利返回平壤。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}